g/resource/Jeff_Garcia\"}, {\"begin\": 4288, \"end\": 4295, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Podence_e_Santa_Combinha\", \"score\": 0.9999735505158263, \"rank\": 2.43188048192189e-05, \"text\": \"Podence\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Podence_e_Santa_Combinha\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Podence_e_Santa_Combinha\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The former Wolves star was standing in an offside position at the time as he went on to deliver the cross for the eventual goal.\", \"from\": 4304, \"to\": 4432, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It means that the goal would have been disallowed for offside, meaning VAR returned to the earlier passage of play.\", \"from\": 4434, \"to\": 4549, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4506, \"end\": 4509, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0149638504672739e-48, \"text\": \"VAR\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So it instead went back to the handball incident, giving the penalty after cameras picked up Garcia handling the ball.\", \"from\": 4551, \"to\": 4669, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4645, \"end\": 4651, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeff_Garcia\", \"score\": 0.5460341813699825, \"rank\": 0.8313871807276146, \"text\": \"Garcia\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q14128148\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeff_Garcia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeff_Garcia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Got all that?\", \"from\": 4671, \"to\": 4684, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Me neither.\", \"from\": 4685, \"to\": 4696, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ayoub El Kaabi scored Olympiacos' penalty after a confusing moment of play  REUTERS  However, disaster struck moments after El Kaabi's goal as Santiago Hezze was shown a second yellow card for an innocuous foul.\", \"from\": 4698, \"to\": 4909, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4699, \"end\": 4713, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ayoub_El_Kaabi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ayoub El Kaabi\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ayoub_El_Kaabi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ayoub_El_Kaabi\"}, {\"begin\": 4721, \"end\": 4731, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiacos_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.37547537910349e-19, \"text\": \"Olympiacos\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiacos_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiacos_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 4842, \"end\": 4850, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santiago\", \"score\": 0.9945459175641476, \"rank\": 0.004434779695536927, \"text\": \"Santiago\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santiago\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Santiago\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It saw the Greek side reduced to 10 men before further controversy in Catalonia.\", \"from\": 4911, \"to\": 4991, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4923, \"end\": 4928, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_language\", \"score\": 0.9945941962421494, \"rank\": 0.005238955737863193, \"text\": \"Greek\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_language\"}, {\"begin\": 4982, \"end\": 4991, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catalonia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.999978755332566, \"rank\": 2.1245039066048662e-05, \"text\": \"Catalonia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catalonia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catalonia_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Marcus Rashford raced through on goal minutes later only to be taken down by Olympiacos goalkeeper Konstantinos Tzolakis.\", \"from\": 4993, \"to\": 5114, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4994, \"end\": 5000, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcus_Aurelius\", \"score\": 0.992881070979226, \"rank\": 0.007169971530862389, \"text\": \"Marcus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcus_Aurelius\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcus_Aurelius\"}, {\"begin\": 5071, \"end\": 5081, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiacos_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.37547537910349e-19, \"text\": \"Olympiacos\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiacos_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiacos_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 5093, \"end\": 5105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Konstantinos_Tzanes\", \"score\": 0.9996643374993026, \"rank\": 0.00033425928016185265, \"text\": \"Konstantinos\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Konstantinos_Tzanes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Konstantinos_Tzanes\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the Manchester United loanee appeared to have knocked the ball past the keeper and had lost control of it before he was brought down.\", \"from\": 5116, \"to\": 5258, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5130, \"end\": 5147, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manchester_United_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.8598082977336263e-22, \"text\": \"Manchester United\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manchester_United_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manchester_United_F.C.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nevertheless, the referee was sent to the pitchside monitor for a second time before giving the penalty.\", \"from\": 5260, \"to\": 5364, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lamine Yamal made no mistake, making it 3-1 after earlier goals from Fermin Lopez in the first half.\", \"from\": 5366, \"to\": 5466, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5374, \"end\": 5379, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yamal_Peninsula\", \"score\": 0.9999836483816514, \"rank\": 1.6351885527647595e-05, \"text\": \"Yamal\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yamal_Peninsula\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yamal_Peninsula\"}, {\"begin\": 5436, \"end\": 5442, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fermin\", \"score\": 0.9999999955089152, \"rank\": 4.491222346686462e-09, \"text\": \"Fermin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fermin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fermin\"}, {\"begin\": 5443, \"end\": 5448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Lopez\", \"score\": 0.9845809731292302, \"rank\": 0.013193883173410189, \"text\": \"Lopez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Lopez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Lopez\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"El Kaabi pulls one back for Olympiacos!His first Champions League goal of the season makes it 2-1 \\u26bd\\ufe0f\\ud83d\\udcfa@tntsports&@discoveryplusUKpic.twitter.com/FUmYWipzcy  Rashford then went on to score himself to put the game to bed, continuing his fine form at Barcelona before Lopez completed his hat-trick with a venomous strike.\", \"from\": 5468, \"to\": 5785, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5518, \"end\": 5534, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Champions_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.371489217750977e-41, \"text\": \"Champions League\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Champions_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Champions_League\"}, {\"begin\": 5717, \"end\": 5726, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Barcelona\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0330451445205924e-15, \"text\": \"Barcelona\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Barcelona\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FC_Barcelona\"}, {\"begin\": 5734, \"end\": 5739, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Lopez\", \"score\": 0.9845809731292302, \"rank\": 0.013193883173410189, \"text\": \"Lopez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Lopez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Lopez\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The England international got another before full-time, making it four goals in the Champions League after his double against Newcastle earlier in the season.\", \"from\": 5787, \"to\": 5945, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5793, \"end\": 5814, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.57980730263562e-17, \"text\": \"England international\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 5873, \"end\": 5889, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Champions_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.371489217750977e-41, \"text\": \"Champions League\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Champions_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Champions_League\"}, {\"begin\": 5915, \"end\": 5924, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newcastle_United_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0644117180965375e-17, \"text\": \"Newcastle\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newcastle_United_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newcastle_United_F.C.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Our Standards:The GB News Editorial Charter\", \"fr